SUMMARY:#PlantWednesday Spotlight
DESCRIPTION:Join our horticulture team every Wednesday for a tour diving into a plant in its peak\, gardening tips\, and more. \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nWednesdays\, 11-11:30 AM | Free with admission or membership \n\n\n\nThe #PlantWednesday Spotlight is a unique “show & tell” program featuring different captivating topics every month. Meet Lan Su’s horticulture team each Wednesday to explore\, learn\, and connect with the natural beauty of Lan Su. These are short 30-min sessions that showcase a horticultural wonder\, technique\, or tool that our passionate horticulturists want to share with fellow plant enthusiasts. Each session will shine a light on the behind-the-scenes operations of the garden\, highlight a plant at its peak beauty\, or focus on recent improvements to our collection. \n\n\n\nEach session will explore a different part of the garden based on that week’s topic. When you arrive\, please check in with the front door staff or volunteers for the exact location to meet in. \n\n\n\n\nGet Admission\n\n\n\n\nThis program is FREE with garden admission or membership. No registration needed.
URL:https://lansugarden.org/event/plant-wednesday-spotlight/2026-03-18/
LOCATION:Lan Su Chinese Garden\, 239 NW Everett Street\, Portland\, Oregon\, 97209
CATEGORIES:Free with admission or membership,Horticulture,Tours
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://lansugarden.org/wp-content/uploads/PlantWednesday-Spotlight-hidden-garden.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Lan Su Chinese Garden":MAILTO:info@lansugarden.org
END:VEVENT
