SUMMARY:Artist Member Hour
DESCRIPTION:First Tuesdays\, 9:00-10:00 AM (Starting December 1\, 2025) \n\n\n\nThis extended garden access gives Artist Members the opportunity to set up tools such as easels and tripods for focused creative expression. \n\n\n\n*Please note that the Artist Hour is exclusively for Artist Members and is intended as a dedicated time for creative activity. \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nWhat is the Artist Membership?\n\n\n\nThe Artist Membership provides benefits created specifically for artists\, including additional access to Lan Su\, the ability to sell photos and paintings of the garden\, and invitations to events tailored for artists.  \n\n\n\n\nExplore Artist Membership
URL:https://lansugarden.org/event/artist-member-hour-5/2026-04-07/
